"""
    Listing all services, and check if created service is present
    """
api = Icinga2API(username=constants.username, password=constants.password,
    url=constants.url, debug=False)
response = api.services.list(hostname=constants.TestHost_data['attrs']['name'])
assert constants.TestHost_data['attrs']['name'
    ] + '!' + constants.TestService_name in response.values()
pytest.mark.run(order=5)
